def: A maker or adapter of plays.
The three anterior ambulacra of echinoderms, collectively.
A kind of spider monkey (Ateles chameck), having the thumbsrudimentary and without a nail.
A soldier of the ancient Muscovite guard or Russian standingarmy; also, the guard itself.
Half clear, or imperfectly transparent; as, a semipellucid gem.
The bending or twining of any part of a plant toward one sideor the other, or in any direction from the vertical.
The quality or state of being viscid; also, that which isviscid; glutinous concretion; stickiness.
A scheme or desire to unite all the Slavic races into oneconfederacy.
The state of being at one or reconciled. [Obs.] Bp. Hall.
